reviewText: I can rewatch this movie and never get tired of it. In fact that's why I got the bku ray over the DVD because it'll last longer. I introduced it to my nieces in middle school and they loved it.
LOVE THIS MOVIE, THE MOVIE IS VERY FUNNY.
Jennifer Garner is one awesome and beautiful actress!!! I love all her movies, but this one she was totally hilarious!!! Absoluetly  loved it!!!
